Package users

Interface IStaffMember

All Superinterfaces:
IUser
All Known Implementing Classes:
Staff
public interface IStaffMember
extends IUser
Interface defining the contract for staff-specific functionality. This interface extends the base functionality provided by IUser with methods specific to staff management, such as GUID, weekly hours, and maximum modules.
